languages.text: {n}Экипаж изумленно молчит. Наконец Вигдис, хрипло вздохнув, тихо изрекает:{/n} "Я вызову слуг для уборки. В остальном вахта прошла без происшествий".

{n}The crew watches in stunned silence. Finally, Vigdis sighs hoarsely and mutters under her breath,{/n} "I will summon the servitors to clean up the bridge. Apart from this incident, the watch was uneventful."

languages.text: {n}Stupéfait, l'équipage observe la scène en silence. Enfin, Vigdis pousse un soupir et marmonne d'une voix rauque :{/n} « Je vais appeler les servitors pour qu'ils nettoient la passerelle. À part cet incident, il ne s'est rien passé de spécial pendant le quart. »

languages.text: {n}所有船员都目瞪口呆，一言不发。到了最后，维格迪斯嘶哑地叹了口气，低声开了口。{/n}“我会叫机仆过来清理舰桥。除了眼下这起事故之外，整个轮班过程风平浪静。”
languages.original_text: {n}The crew watches in stunned silence. Finally, Vigdis sighs hoarsely and mutters under her breath,{/n} "I will summon the servitors to clean up the bridge. Apart from this incident, the watch was uneventful."

traits.locale_text: {n}所有船员目瞪口呆。到了最后，维格迪斯嘶哑地叹了口气，低声开了口。{/n}“我会叫奴工过来清理舰桥。除了这件事情之外，整个轮班过程风平浪静。”

languages.text: {n}Die Crew sieht entsetzt schweigend zu. Schließlich seufzt Vigdis heiser und murmelt:{/n} "Ich werde die Servitoren rufen, um die Brücke zu reinigen. Von diesem Zwischenfall abgesehen, war die Wache ereignislos."
languages.original_text: {n}The crew watches in stunned silence. Finally, Vigdis sighs hoarsely and mutters under her breath,{/n} "I will summon the servitors to clean up the bridge. Apart from this incident, the watch was uneventful."

traits.locale_text: {n}Die Crew sieht entsetzt schweigend zu. Schließlich seufzt Vigdis heiser und murmelt:{/n} "Ich werde die Servitoren rufen, um die Brücke zu reinigen. Ansonsten war die Wache ereignislos."

languages.text: {n}La tripulación observa en completo silencio. Finalmente, Vigdis suspira con voz ronca y murmura entre dientes:{/n} «Indicaré a los servidores que limpien el puente. Aparte de esto, la guardia ha transcurrido sin incidentes».
languages.original_text: {n}The crew watches in stunned silence. Finally, Vigdis sighs hoarsely and mutters under her breath,{/n} "I will summon the servitors to clean up the bridge. Apart from this incident, the watch was uneventful."

traits.locale_text: {n}La tripulación observa en completo silencio. Finalmente, Vigdis suspira con voz ronca y murmura entre dientes:{/n} «Indicaré a los servidores que limpien el puente. Si no, la guardia habría ocurrido sin incidentes».

languages.text: {n}クルーたちは仰天した沈黙の中で見守る。最後に、ヴィグディスはかすれた声でつぶやく。{/n}「サーヴィターを呼んでブリッジを片付けさせます。この件、以外には特に何事もありませんでした」
languages.original_text: {n}The crew watches in stunned silence. Finally, Vigdis sighs hoarsely and mutters under her breath,{/n} "I will summon the servitors to clean up the bridge. Apart from this incident, the watch was uneventful."

languages.text: {n}Taş kesilen mürettebat, olan biteni sessizce izliyor. Nihayetinde Vigdis, boğuk bir sesle iç çekip mırıldanıyor.{/n} "Köprüyü temizlesinler diye hizmetörleri çağıracağım. Bu hadiseyi saymazsak olaysız bir nöbet geçirdik."
languages.original_text: {n}The crew watches in stunned silence. Finally, Vigdis sighs hoarsely and mutters under her breath,{/n} "I will summon the servitors to clean up the bridge. Apart from this incident, the watch was uneventful."

traits.locale_text: {n}Mürettebat taş kesilmiş hâlde, sessizce izliyor. Nihayetinde Vigdis boğuk bir sesle iç çekiyor ve mırıldanıyor:{/n} "Köprüyü temizlesinler diye servitörleri çağıracağım. Bu olay haricinde nöbet olaysız geçti."
